-- Germany Helping Stabilize World Economy by Recovering, Merkel Tells BDI
-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 2010-09-28T10:09:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/germany-helping-stabilize-world-economy-by-recovering-merkel-tells-bdi.html
Germany is helping shore up the
global economy with its recovery, Chancellor Angela Merkel said.  “We are stabilizing not just our own economy but are
taking care of our international responsibilities,” Merkel told
a conference of the BDI German industry association in Berlin
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
